name: International Conference on Science, Engineering & Technology
content: The foremost aspiration International Conference on Science, Engineering & Technology, is to serve as a platform that facilitates the deliberation of the challenges involved in the practical implementation of all the most advanced knowledge produced in the fields of science, advanced engineering and technology. The organizers of this highly anticipated event look forward to bringing all specialists, academics, practitioners, industry experts and students (from the fields of science, engineering, and technology) from around the world together and expose the results of modern experimental research studies in these disciplines for their benefit.
